sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant DB

User->>Frontend: Search employees
Frontend->>API: GET /api/employees/search
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: Validate start_time and end_time
alt Only one of start_time/end_time provided
API-->>Frontend: 400 Both start_time and end_time are required together
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Both provided or both absent
alt Invalid start_time or end_time format
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid start_time or end_time format
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Valid time filters
alt end_time <= start_time
API-->>Frontend: 400 end_time must be greater than start_time
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Filters valid
API->>DB: Execute search query with filters
alt DB error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
else Success
DB-->>API: rows
API-->>Frontend: 200 employee results
Frontend-->>User: Render results
end
end
end
end
end
